      • addTour

        public void addTour(Tour tour)
        Adds a solution to this TSPLIB problem instance. This method does not verify that the solution has all required edges; the caller must ensure this condition holds.
        Parameters:
        tour - the solution to add

      • addTour

        public void addTour(java.io.File file)
             throws java.io.IOException
        Adds a solution to this TSPLIB problem instance that is defined in a separate file. This method does not verify that the solution is a valid tour for this problem instance; the caller must ensure this condition holds.
        Parameters:
        file - the file containing a solution to this TSPLIB problem instance
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurred while loading the tour
